---
import Aurora from "@components/backgrounds/Aurora.astro";
import Button from "@components/Button.astro";
import BackIcon from "@components/icons/BackIcon.astro";
import LayoutExample from "@layouts/LayoutExample.astro";
---

<LayoutExample title="Aurora">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full z-0 bg-black">
    <Aurora />
  </div>

  <div
    class="relative grow flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-w-full min-h-full text-white z-10"
  >
    <h1>Aurora</h1>
    <Button class="mt-6" onclick="window.location='/'"><BackIcon /></Button>
  </div>

  <Fragment slot="extra">
    <section class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col">
      <a class="sticky top-0 inline-block p-4 z-10" href="/"
        ><BackIcon class="text-cyan-900 mt-1.5 w-12 h-12" /></a
      >
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full -z-10 bg-black">
        <Aurora
          colorStops={["#DE3163", "#CCCCFF", "#FFBF00"]}
          amplitude={0.1}
          speed={3.0}
        />
      </div>
      <div class="content mx-auto -mt-20 ms-20 p-4 text-white">
        <p>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Assumenda
          velit sequi veritatis officiis explicabo asperiores soluta ex quis
          perferendis dolor consequatur ea nam odio, praesentium, laboriosam,
          recusandae doloremque fuga nemo.
        </p>
        <p>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Inventore
          sed, atque impedit asperiores eligendi non commodi ab dolorum in nihil
          minus accusantium aliquam esse amet labore cum voluptates reiciendis
          tenetur, ea, ipsa suscipit molestiae doloremque! Totam est obcaecati
          fugiat magnam dolore ex perferendis suscipit molestiae in magni nisi
          impedit vel esse quod neque aut ut, quasi ipsa optio eveniet? Sunt et
          dolore quia voluptatibus dignissimos omnis atque aut doloribus
